		<h2><a href="http://paxlupo.com/2013/09/03/it-goes-without-saying-2/" rel="bookmark">It Goes Without&nbsp;Saying.</a></h2>
		<div class="date">September 3, 2013</div>
	</div><!--end post header-->
	<div class="meta clear">
		<div class="tags"></div>
		<div class="author">
					</div>
	</div><!--end meta-->
	<div class="entry clear">
				<p><a href="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/09/wires-712x800.jpg"><img class="alignleft  wp-image-950" alt="wires (712x800)" src="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/09/wires-712x800.jpg?w=288&#038;h=323" width="288" height="323" /></a>I took an afternoon nap<br />
During the storm that killed a man in Dade.</p>
<p>I dreamt of a world where everyone misunderstood everything.</p>
<p>Awakening, the clock said 8:05.<br />
&#8220;How strange and beautiful&#8221; I thought<br />
&#8220;That it should be so dark in the morning.&#8221;</p>
<hr />
<p>Thank You for your consideration.<br />
