<div id="post-910" class="post-910 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-social-commentary tag-buddhist tag-giorno tag-morrison tag-religion tag-spirituality tag-three-jewels">
	<div class="post-header">
		<h2><a href="http://paxlupo.com/2013/08/23/forest-and-factory/" rel="bookmark">Forest and Factory</a></h2>
		<div class="date">August 23, 2013</div>
	</div><!--end post header-->
	<div class="meta clear">
		<div class="tags">tags: <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/buddhist/" rel="tag">buddhist</a>, <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/giorno/" rel="tag">giorno</a>, <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/morrison/" rel="tag">morrison</a>, <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/religion/" rel="tag">religion</a>, <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/spirituality/" rel="tag">spirituality</a>, <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/three-jewels/" rel="tag">three jewels</a></div>
		<div class="author">
					</div>
	</div><!--end meta-->
	<div class="entry clear">
				<h1>The Three Jewels.</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong>What does the word ‘<em>refuge</em>’ mean?</strong></a></h2>
<p><a href="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/5880353861_670bbe912a_z.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-913 alignnone" alt="5880353861_670bbe912a_z" src="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/5880353861_670bbe912a_z.jpg?w=600"   /></a></p>
<p><strong>I take refuge in the Buddha who shows me the way.<br />
</strong><em>The way through the forest is not the same as the way through the factory.</em></p>
<p><strong>I take refuge in the Dharma of wisdom and understanding.</strong><br />
<em>The Dharma is the wisdom of all time. This is our particular time.</em></p>
<p><strong>I take refuge in the Sanga, with harmony and peace.</strong><br />
<em>I wish you well.<br />
</em><em>Cultivate compassion where there is no water or soil.<br />
The landscape is a dust bowl.<br />
&#8220;A noble effort, doomed, but the only choice.&#8221; ~Giorno</em></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>&#8220;We’re lost in a Roman wilderness of pain.&#8221;</strong><br />
<a href="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/5880355837_acde0ff4d4_z.jpg"><img class=" wp-image-924 alignnone" alt="5880355837_acde0ff4d4_z" src="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/5880355837_acde0ff4d4_z.jpg?w=393&#038;h=518" width="393" height="518" /></a></p>
<hr />
<p><strong><em>One cannot take refuge and brave the storm at the same time.</em></strong></p>
<p><a href="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/5880355943_7f97373e5e_o1.jpg"><img class="size-full wp-image-920 alignnone" alt="5880355943_7f97373e5e_o" src="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/5880355943_7f97373e5e_o1.jpg?w=600"   /></a></p>
<hr />
<p>Thank You for your consideration.<br />
