<div id="post-902" class="post-902 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-social-commentary tag-buddhist tag-reincarnation">
	<div class="post-header">
		<h2><a href="http://paxlupo.com/2013/08/19/buddhist-reincarnation-in-six-obvious-steps/" rel="bookmark">Buddhist Reincarnation in Six Obvious&nbsp;Steps</a></h2>
		<div class="date">August 19, 2013</div>
	</div><!--end post header-->
	<div class="meta clear">
		<div class="tags">tags: <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/buddhist/" rel="tag">buddhist</a>, <a href="http://paxlupo.com/tag/reincarnation/" rel="tag">reincarnation</a></div>
		<div class="author">
					</div>
	</div><!--end meta-->
	<div class="entry clear">
				<h3>Buddhist Reincarnation in Six Obvious Steps</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>1. You&#8217;re born.</strong></li>
<li><strong>2. You spend a lifetime making a gawd-awful mess of things.</strong></li>
<li><strong>3. You die.</strong></li>
<li><strong>4. Another iteration of your form emerges into the previous mess you made.</strong></li>
<li><strong>5. Since you don&#8217;t remember a thing, you blame the mess on everyone else.</strong></li>
<li><strong>6. Go to step 1.</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><a href="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/haywain_central_panel_of_the_triptych_wga.jpg"><img src="http://paxlupo.files.wordpress.com/2013/08/haywain_central_panel_of_the_triptych_wga.jpg?w=600&#038;h=835" alt="Haywain_central_panel_of_the_triptych_WGA"   class="alignleft size-large wp-image-905" /></a></p>
